WEBVTT

01:26.600 --> 01:35.000
[LIVE UP TO YOUR YOUTH]

01:35.370 --> 01:37.800
[Episode 16]

01:38.229 --> 01:39.830
I, Tao Baohua, am the only one

01:40.370 --> 01:42.030
that is allowed to beat my son.

01:43.009 --> 01:43.700
No one else

01:44.789 --> 01:46.280
can lay a finger on you.

01:47.400 --> 01:49.229
Should I come back again tomorrow?

01:49.229 --> 01:50.729
Why wouldn't you come back?

01:50.729 --> 01:54.479
[Business Time: 5:30 a.m.]

01:52.140 --> 01:53.800
If I come back a few more times,

01:54.259 --> 01:55.640
our family's business

01:56.370 --> 01:57.500
will be ruined by me.

02:01.260 --> 02:02.120
Don't worry.

02:03.920 --> 02:05.730
It will all be yours eventually.

02:07.850 --> 02:09.380
Whether it's ruined or not,

02:09.810 --> 02:11.150
it's up to you.

02:13.000 --> 02:13.610
Dad,

02:14.300 --> 02:15.060
actually,

02:17.060 --> 02:17.910
I'm used to it.

02:19.370 --> 02:20.370
You're used to it?

02:20.840 --> 02:21.770
What do you mean?

02:24.360 --> 02:26.490
Actually, I'm just a lousy performer.

02:28.530 --> 02:29.530
Over the years,

02:31.030 --> 02:33.410
I've gotten used to
how people from outside

02:33.410 --> 02:34.160
treat me.

02:46.240 --> 02:46.970
Liangliang.

02:48.780 --> 02:50.380
Let me just ask you one thing.

02:52.520 --> 02:56.020
So you can just endure something like this

02:56.500 --> 02:58.700
and keep enduring it without giving up?

03:01.100 --> 03:02.230
I've made up my mind.

03:04.530 --> 03:05.530
I can do it myself.

03:07.420 --> 03:08.750
No matter how hard it is,

03:09.740 --> 03:12.200
I still have to stick to the path
I've chosen.

03:29.090 --> 03:29.560
I got it.

03:34.530 --> 03:35.290
Thanks, Dad.

03:35.410 --> 03:38.090
[Business Time: 5:30 a.m.]

03:56.710 --> 03:58.090
I feel like I'm cursed.

03:58.120 --> 03:59.250
I have such bad luck.

04:00.060 --> 04:01.660
My saxophone fell and broke.

04:02.470 --> 04:03.270
What's wrong?

04:03.340 --> 04:04.840
So your saxophone is broken?

04:04.840 --> 04:05.390
Well,

04:06.080 --> 04:07.340
I accidentally dropped it,

04:07.340 --> 04:08.740
and now it's leaking air.

04:12.780 --> 04:13.870
No, no, no!

04:13.900 --> 04:14.830
Stop playing it!

04:15.040 --> 04:16.190
Just spare me.

04:16.310 --> 04:17.990
I have an orchestra audition
in a few days.

04:16.410 --> 04:20.240
[Endeavor]

04:18.360 --> 04:19.060
I can't borrow one from others.

04:19.060 --> 04:20.320
Who would lend it to me?

04:20.500 --> 04:22.440
You're still going to the audition?

04:22.440 --> 04:29.730
[Endeavor]

04:22.920 --> 04:23.790
I have to.

04:23.920 --> 04:25.740
Even if all orchestra auditions
in the world were rigged,

04:25.740 --> 04:26.500
I would still have to try.

04:26.500 --> 04:27.420
When the results are out,

04:27.420 --> 04:28.270
my name will be there,

04:28.270 --> 04:29.730
and they'll feel ashamed.

04:35.720 --> 04:36.980
How should I repair it?

04:40.000 --> 04:41.400
You're driving me crazy.

04:46.060 --> 04:48.190
This money is enough to repair it, huh?

04:53.130 --> 04:54.330
I'm lending it to you.

04:55.070 --> 04:56.720
Just repair your saxophone properly.

04:56.720 --> 04:57.680
This sounds like

04:57.830 --> 04:59.090
it has a great mission.

05:03.570 --> 05:04.620
As screenwriters,

05:04.620 --> 05:05.800
you can make so much money, huh?

05:05.800 --> 05:06.540
Where did you

05:07.120 --> 05:07.980
get this money?

05:08.130 --> 05:09.370
None of your business.

05:09.370 --> 05:11.230
I bought a lottery ticket and won.

05:13.180 --> 05:15.980
I didn't say you wouldn't
have to return the money.

05:16.160 --> 05:18.190
I also didn't say
I wouldn't return the money.

05:18.190 --> 05:19.870
I just think...

05:20.480 --> 05:21.360
Just take it.

05:21.690 --> 05:23.190
You are from Beijing anyway.

05:23.190 --> 05:23.870
If there's a penny less

05:23.870 --> 05:25.180
when you return the money,

05:25.180 --> 05:26.040
I will go to your house

05:26.040 --> 05:27.300
and ask your mom for it.

05:27.330 --> 05:27.770
Fine.

05:28.750 --> 05:29.620
You can ask my mom, my dad

05:29.620 --> 05:31.080
or whoever you want for it.

05:31.300 --> 05:32.420
But this time,

05:32.510 --> 05:34.370
you've really done me a big favor.

05:34.830 --> 05:35.730
Thank you, Xu.

05:35.870 --> 05:36.290
No.

05:37.500 --> 05:38.100
Thank you,

05:38.540 --> 05:39.070
Mr. Xu.

05:39.720 --> 05:41.070
I'll go make a call now

05:41.070 --> 05:42.070
to contact the parts supplier.

05:42.070 --> 05:42.630
Just go.

05:42.630 --> 05:43.300
Well...

05:43.830 --> 05:46.100
Dear friend, I'll return your favor later.

05:46.100 --> 05:46.960
Thanks, Mr. Xu!

06:00.120 --> 06:00.570
Honey!

06:01.510 --> 06:01.940
Honey!

06:03.070 --> 06:03.620
Hurry up!

06:03.870 --> 06:04.250
What's wrong?

06:04.250 --> 06:04.980
Look at this.

06:09.810 --> 06:11.060
Well, what a broad smile you have.

06:11.060 --> 06:12.400
W-Where did you get

06:12.570 --> 06:13.570
so much money?

06:13.810 --> 06:15.480
Your son sent it to us.

06:15.540 --> 06:16.710
Our son sent it to us?

06:17.740 --> 06:19.390
He also wrote on the postscript

06:19.390 --> 06:20.920
that we should buy two sets

06:20.950 --> 06:22.220
of nice clothes.

06:22.560 --> 06:23.490
How much is this?

06:23.560 --> 06:24.420
5,000 yuan.

06:24.620 --> 06:25.280
5,000 yuan?

06:26.220 --> 06:28.620
Using 5,000 yuan
to buy two sets of clothes?

06:29.450 --> 06:30.710
Are they dragon robes?

06:31.030 --> 06:31.360
Well,

06:31.370 --> 06:33.540
he didn't ask us to spend it all.

06:38.100 --> 06:38.970
I got it.

06:41.040 --> 06:42.010
This boy...

06:44.870 --> 06:46.930
is trying to make me angry on purpose.

06:47.770 --> 06:49.659
You are so narrow-minded.

06:50.370 --> 06:50.950
This boy

06:50.980 --> 06:51.800
sent so much money to us.

06:51.800 --> 06:53.430
He's being filial, you know?

06:53.480 --> 06:54.240
Being filial?

06:54.240 --> 06:54.950
Besides,

06:55.450 --> 06:56.800
this 5,000 yuan can prove

06:56.800 --> 06:57.360
that he is doing quite well

06:57.360 --> 06:59.060
in Beijing right now.

06:59.240 --> 07:01.440
If he's really doing well, that's nice.

07:03.360 --> 07:04.220
Could it be that

07:04.770 --> 07:06.300
he is not on the right track?

07:07.800 --> 07:09.260
Don't think of everything

07:09.430 --> 07:10.390
in such a...

07:11.060 --> 07:12.690
As his father,

07:12.860 --> 07:14.470
how could you say that about your son?

07:14.470 --> 07:16.190
-I'm worried about him. Why can't I...
-You are not...

07:16.190 --> 07:17.480
Y-Your son isn't

07:17.480 --> 07:18.300
someone like that.

07:18.300 --> 07:20.040
Besides, what kind of place is Beijing?

07:20.040 --> 07:21.390
Beijing is heaven.

07:22.660 --> 07:24.140
Alright.

07:24.740 --> 07:25.500
We'll look on the bright side.

07:25.500 --> 07:25.960
Okay?

07:29.180 --> 07:30.060
What should we do now?

07:30.060 --> 07:31.060
Let's do as he said

07:31.690 --> 07:33.020
and go buy some clothes.

07:33.370 --> 07:34.370
Let's go buy some clothes.

07:34.370 --> 07:35.370
-Let's go!
-Come on!

07:35.370 --> 07:37.100
Let's eat at a restaurant, too.

07:38.159 --> 07:39.810
I'm tired of cooking.

07:42.190 --> 07:43.860
Let's find the best restaurant.

07:43.860 --> 07:45.180
Yes, let's find one with

07:45.180 --> 07:46.070
a really bright storefront.

07:46.070 --> 07:47.250
We'll order the most expensive dishes.

07:47.250 --> 07:47.620
Yes!

07:47.750 --> 07:48.480
Is that okay?

07:48.750 --> 07:50.070
Then the owner of this restaurant

07:50.070 --> 07:51.670
will be overjoyed, won't he?

07:52.060 --> 07:53.240
At night... At night, he'll be so happy

07:53.240 --> 07:55.450
even in his dreams.

07:55.659 --> 07:56.659
Great.

07:58.159 --> 07:58.720
What are you looking at?

07:58.720 --> 07:59.520
You know what?

08:01.360 --> 08:04.100
We should buy you a woolen coat.

08:05.160 --> 08:05.660
We'll buy...

08:05.660 --> 08:07.060
And a pair of riding boots

08:07.630 --> 08:08.290
with heels.

08:09.480 --> 08:10.360
What do you think?

08:10.360 --> 08:11.420
You know what?

08:11.500 --> 08:13.240
A few days ago, I really saw one

08:13.270 --> 08:14.480
at the department store.

08:14.480 --> 08:16.680
-It was very beautiful.
-So you want it?

08:17.930 --> 08:19.010
I'll satisfy you.

08:19.040 --> 08:19.520
Okay.

08:20.300 --> 08:20.800
Let's go.

08:20.800 --> 08:21.330
Let's go.

08:26.010 --> 08:26.810
What's wrong?

08:27.660 --> 08:28.270
Let's go.

08:28.570 --> 08:29.570
Let's not do this.

08:31.330 --> 08:31.960
For us,

08:32.010 --> 08:33.809
just talking about it is enough.

08:34.580 --> 08:36.200
I-I still want to deposit this money

08:36.200 --> 08:37.179
into his...

08:37.650 --> 08:39.820
his previous bankbook.

08:40.270 --> 08:42.500
With this, the bank balance will be almost

08:42.500 --> 08:43.480
10,000 yuan.

08:44.650 --> 08:45.600
Oh, you're...

08:48.000 --> 08:49.360
such a good mother.

08:54.150 --> 08:56.410
We're so lucky to have you in this family.

08:58.740 --> 08:59.650
Being with me,

09:00.720 --> 09:01.980
you've suffered a lot.

09:02.000 --> 09:02.930
That's not true.

09:03.630 --> 09:04.490
How about this?

09:05.360 --> 09:06.790
We'll deposit the money in the bank
for our kid first.

09:06.790 --> 09:07.920
Let's do as you said.

09:08.370 --> 09:09.520
When I get my salary,

09:10.870 --> 09:11.800
I'll definitely

09:12.370 --> 09:13.500
buy you a new outfit.

09:14.340 --> 09:15.050
Is that okay?

09:15.050 --> 09:15.390
Okay.

09:15.720 --> 09:17.920
I feel more at ease spending your money.

09:18.440 --> 09:19.530
I'll go deposit this in the bank now.

09:19.530 --> 09:20.040
Just go.

09:48.170 --> 09:49.170
Thank you so much.

09:50.100 --> 09:51.270
So this is the Seasons Change Hostel

09:51.270 --> 09:52.330
you've mentioned?

09:52.480 --> 09:53.030
Yes.

09:53.340 --> 09:55.200
But we still have to go further in.

09:57.200 --> 09:58.650
Alright. I'm not going in.

09:58.650 --> 09:59.840
I'll just drop you off here.

09:59.840 --> 10:00.320
Mr. Chu,

10:01.510 --> 10:02.110
thank you.

10:03.270 --> 10:04.720
You're saying this again.

10:04.720 --> 10:05.770
There's nothing to thank me for.

10:05.770 --> 10:06.830
You're excellent,

10:07.100 --> 10:08.560
so the director chose you.

10:08.740 --> 10:09.800
I know

10:10.130 --> 10:11.500
without your help,

10:11.860 --> 10:13.720
I wouldn't have gotten this role.

10:15.120 --> 10:17.190
This role isn't too big or too small.

10:17.410 --> 10:18.810
It's just a normal favor.

10:19.410 --> 10:20.170
If it's helpful

10:20.170 --> 10:21.390
for your acting career,

10:21.390 --> 10:23.120
I can do even more in the future.

10:23.290 --> 10:25.320
You've already helped me quite enough.

10:25.320 --> 10:27.520
I have to work hard by myself from now on.

10:30.240 --> 10:31.970
Let me give you a little advice.

10:32.470 --> 10:33.200
You'd better

10:33.410 --> 10:35.220
listen more to experienced people.

10:35.220 --> 10:37.420
This way, you can avoid taking detours.

10:39.030 --> 10:39.460
Yes.

10:41.440 --> 10:42.170
Bye, Mr. Chu.

10:42.480 --> 10:42.940
Bye.

10:56.650 --> 10:59.370
[The Late Love,
written by He Sheng & Xu Shengli]

11:01.230 --> 11:01.740
[Dimly, a shadow was shaking.]

11:01.760 --> 11:02.400
[Night Cat
walked into the factory gently.]

11:02.430 --> 11:02.960
[A moment later,
there was a terrible scream.]

11:34.710 --> 11:36.830
[Abandoned]

11:54.050 --> 11:58.070
[It kept crawling and staring.]

12:03.460 --> 12:06.910
[The Late Love,
written by He Sheng & Xu Shengli]

12:24.900 --> 12:27.930
[To the General Editorial Office
of Jinnan Film Studio]

12:32.220 --> 12:32.820
Good luck!

12:33.080 --> 12:34.810
Xu Shengli, the screenwriter.

12:39.010 --> 12:40.410
Every time I pass by here,

12:40.650 --> 12:41.650
I always feel that

12:42.700 --> 12:44.230
before pursuing my dreams,

12:44.530 --> 12:46.190
I still have to survive first.

12:47.580 --> 12:49.620
You have to consider it
the other way around.

12:49.620 --> 12:51.190
This is also a reminder that

12:51.270 --> 12:53.680
all paths will meet again eventually.

12:55.320 --> 12:56.050
Definitely.

13:00.300 --> 13:06.040
[End-of-term Performance
of Beijing Conservatory of Music]

13:02.200 --> 13:03.060
Zhuang Zhuang.

13:05.050 --> 13:05.780
Give it a try.

13:06.500 --> 13:07.630
There's still a little bit
of the original track

13:07.630 --> 13:09.490
which I really couldn't cover up.

13:09.650 --> 13:10.580
So they're mine?

13:13.510 --> 13:16.920
[Small Auditorium]

13:13.630 --> 13:14.720
Thank you, Xu Shengli.

13:14.720 --> 13:15.340
Not at all.

13:15.940 --> 13:16.860
This is the first time

13:16.860 --> 13:18.520
I've had my own backing track.

13:19.290 --> 13:20.440
In the future,

13:20.940 --> 13:21.750
you'll be

13:21.750 --> 13:22.480
accompanied

13:22.480 --> 13:23.410
by a whole band,

13:23.430 --> 13:24.230
right in here.

13:33.170 --> 13:34.360
Affected by the

13:34.360 --> 13:36.370
strong cold air mass from Siberia,

13:36.510 --> 13:38.440
North China will recently experience

13:37.460 --> 13:40.560
[Hengtian Non-Staple Food]

13:38.510 --> 13:39.500
a large-scale

13:39.520 --> 13:41.010
sharp drop in temperature.

13:41.010 --> 13:43.870
Many places
have seen the first snow of this winter.

13:46.130 --> 13:49.080
Repairing range hoods!

13:49.120 --> 13:50.650
As an important city

13:50.650 --> 13:51.550
in North China,

13:51.580 --> 13:52.600
Beijing is the first to feel

13:52.600 --> 13:54.060
the power of this cold air.

13:55.720 --> 13:56.650
Meanwhile,

13:56.720 --> 13:58.240
some areas in Northwest China,

13:58.240 --> 14:00.100
as well as Henan, Hebei and other places,

14:00.100 --> 14:01.700
have also ushered in snowy weather.

14:01.700 --> 14:03.900
In Hebei, from Zhangjiakou in the north

14:03.940 --> 14:05.170
to Handan in the south,

14:05.170 --> 14:06.900
a large area is covered by snow.

14:06.960 --> 14:07.700
This snowfall

14:07.700 --> 14:09.050
has caused some highways

14:09.050 --> 14:09.980
to be temporarily closed.

14:09.980 --> 14:10.840
Railway transportation

14:10.840 --> 14:11.410
has also been

14:11.410 --> 14:13.070
affected to varying degrees.

14:14.910 --> 14:15.530
Here!

14:24.150 --> 14:25.240
It's snowing!

14:26.290 --> 14:27.900
It's snowing!

14:28.410 --> 14:29.010
Hurry!

14:30.500 --> 14:32.100
No! You're so underclothed!

14:47.780 --> 14:52.700
[Seasons Change Hostel]

14:49.340 --> 14:49.880
It's so cold.

14:49.880 --> 14:51.460
You're not even wearing a coat.

14:51.460 --> 14:52.480
Here. Put this on.

14:52.480 --> 14:53.240
Look!

14:53.870 --> 14:54.670
When it falls on the clothes,

14:54.670 --> 14:56.370
it really looks like a snowflake.

14:56.370 --> 14:57.840
It's exactly the same
as that in the pictures.

14:57.840 --> 14:59.640
These are snowflakes actually.

15:00.980 --> 15:02.410
Haven't you been to Beijing before?

15:02.410 --> 15:04.030
Why is it still so novel to you?

15:04.030 --> 15:06.030
You think I can always see snow
when I'm in Beijing?

15:06.030 --> 15:06.770
Thank you.

15:06.840 --> 15:07.770
You're welcome.

15:08.720 --> 15:11.700
[Guest Room]

15:11.770 --> 15:12.860
Okay. Fine.

15:11.840 --> 15:13.450
[Seasons Change Hostel]

15:21.650 --> 15:22.130
Well...

15:22.650 --> 15:24.380
Your snowballs are like bombs.

15:25.650 --> 15:26.860
Did I hurt you?

15:43.090 --> 15:46.670
[Seasons Change Hostel]

15:44.750 --> 15:46.320
Anyway, it doesn't hurt
even when you fall down, huh?

15:46.320 --> 15:47.240
I'll give you a suplex.

15:47.240 --> 15:48.440
No! I admit defeat!

15:47.350 --> 15:49.870
[A home away from home, only better.]

15:49.970 --> 15:53.810
[Guest Room]

15:53.860 --> 15:58.430
[Seasons Change Hostel]

15:57.390 --> 15:58.250
I admit defeat!

15:58.390 --> 15:59.270
I admit defeat!

15:58.500 --> 16:03.130
[Guest Room]

15:59.890 --> 16:01.750
I'm not playing with you anymore.

16:04.690 --> 16:05.750
Don't sit down yet.

16:05.890 --> 16:07.620
Let me wipe the snow off for you.

16:08.720 --> 16:09.980
I think after the snow,

16:10.250 --> 16:12.150
the little inn is even more beautiful.

16:12.150 --> 16:13.600
Alright. You can sit now.

16:22.580 --> 16:24.110
The script Mr. He and I wrote

16:24.500 --> 16:25.430
can't be filmed.

16:29.240 --> 16:31.550
This can be considered as my first script

16:31.940 --> 16:34.470
during my career
as a screenwriter in my life.

16:36.470 --> 16:37.120
I still remember

16:37.120 --> 16:38.780
that day, when Mr. He told me

16:39.010 --> 16:39.980
he would also

16:39.980 --> 16:41.200
add my name to the credits,

16:41.200 --> 16:42.120
I was so happy.

16:42.700 --> 16:43.220
I hugged him

16:43.220 --> 16:44.880
and kissed him several times.

16:49.510 --> 16:50.460
In this period of time,

16:50.460 --> 16:52.520
I've been trying to digest this news.

16:55.440 --> 16:56.670
When I came back that day,

16:56.670 --> 16:58.110
I threw the script away.

16:58.840 --> 17:00.640
But I regretted it immediately.

17:01.170 --> 17:02.570
I went back to look for it,

17:02.740 --> 17:04.540
but I couldn't find it anywhere.

17:05.640 --> 17:06.849
Maybe God

17:06.880 --> 17:08.440
wanted to teach me a lesson.

17:10.180 --> 17:11.310
Wait a moment for me.

17:12.890 --> 17:16.510
[Seasons Change Hostel]

17:31.250 --> 17:37.280
[Seasons Change Hostel]

17:39.270 --> 17:39.920
Here.

17:51.010 --> 17:52.250
[The Late Love,
written by He Sheng & Xu Shengli]

17:58.100 --> 17:59.150
How come you...

18:00.330 --> 18:02.060
This is something so precious.

18:02.070 --> 18:03.440
Don't lose it again.

18:08.350 --> 18:10.680
[The Late Love,
written by He Sheng & Xu Shengli]

18:19.330 --> 18:20.350
Alright.

18:19.380 --> 18:24.210
[A home away from home, only better.]

18:21.090 --> 18:22.250
Life is like

18:22.250 --> 18:23.580
stepping into the snow.

18:24.310 --> 18:26.720
It's inevitable to step into it unevenly,

18:26.920 --> 18:28.520
which is completely normal.

18:30.810 --> 18:32.290
But just like you said,

18:33.050 --> 18:34.960
spring will definitely come.

18:36.570 --> 18:37.940
Even if it were not to come,

18:37.940 --> 18:39.400
winter would also be nice.

18:46.070 --> 18:47.930
Actually, in this period of time,

18:48.250 --> 18:49.790
I was ready to give up.

18:53.180 --> 18:55.500
It wasn't until you asked me for help

18:55.500 --> 18:56.750
that I suddenly felt

18:57.940 --> 19:01.000
there was still something
to look forward to in my life.

19:03.270 --> 19:03.830
That was perfect,

19:03.830 --> 19:05.030
so I just took this chance

19:05.030 --> 19:06.960
to hit the pause button for myself.

19:07.290 --> 19:09.020
I sent some money to my parents.

19:10.240 --> 19:13.370
I paid the rent to extend my stay
until after the New Year.

19:14.110 --> 19:15.360
Actually, I feel

19:16.880 --> 19:17.980
quite grounded.

19:20.440 --> 19:21.680
I've also realized that

19:21.680 --> 19:24.780
when a person is down on his luck,

19:26.400 --> 19:28.250
this feeling of being needed

19:29.480 --> 19:31.480
can actually help him save himself.

19:39.310 --> 19:40.170
Zhuang Zhuang.

19:43.750 --> 19:45.610
Thank you for letting me help you.

19:46.160 --> 19:48.160
I know you did it on purpose.

19:49.110 --> 19:50.270
I really needed it.

19:52.140 --> 19:53.070
Alright.

19:58.640 --> 20:00.310
Although saying
that the result doesn't matter

20:00.310 --> 20:02.310
sounds like I'm comforting myself,

20:03.030 --> 20:05.040
I really think that in this world,

20:05.160 --> 20:06.560
no path is walked in vain.

20:08.030 --> 20:10.000
Even going through countless hardships

20:10.000 --> 20:11.640
won't drive me back home.

20:13.550 --> 20:14.440
Right!

20:17.580 --> 20:21.630
[Seasons Change Hostel]

20:26.810 --> 20:27.330
Come in.

20:31.920 --> 20:32.650
You're here.

20:35.140 --> 20:35.920
Mr. Chu.

20:36.290 --> 20:37.460
Didn't you say

20:37.680 --> 20:39.480
Director Huang and the others
would be here too?

20:39.480 --> 20:40.290
I originally arranged for

20:40.290 --> 20:41.900
Director Huang and the others to come.

20:41.900 --> 20:43.700
But something came up for them
at the last minute.

20:43.700 --> 20:45.430
They're really unable to come.

20:46.980 --> 20:48.400
Hey, come in.

20:52.270 --> 20:52.800
Sit down.

20:59.380 --> 21:00.110
Have a drink.

21:04.400 --> 21:05.140
Thank you.

21:07.750 --> 21:08.810
I'm quite grateful

21:08.880 --> 21:10.340
that you could come today.

21:10.700 --> 21:11.240
Really.

21:13.400 --> 21:15.530
Today, I'm so eager to talk to someone.

21:16.830 --> 21:17.630
You know what?

21:19.510 --> 21:21.370
A movie I invested in two years ago

21:22.440 --> 21:24.300
is confirmed to lose money today.

21:26.420 --> 21:27.420
Four million yuan

21:28.850 --> 21:29.440
is gone.

21:32.270 --> 21:33.200
Let me tell you.

21:36.250 --> 21:38.050
Before I invested in this movie,

21:38.200 --> 21:39.330
there was a director

21:40.200 --> 21:42.000
who desperately tried to tell me

21:42.070 --> 21:44.000
that he wanted to use a new actress.

21:46.070 --> 21:47.500
In the end, this actress

21:48.070 --> 21:49.240
could neither act

21:49.460 --> 21:50.880
nor understand the role.

21:51.550 --> 21:53.150
If a movie isn't convincing,

21:54.510 --> 21:56.040
how could it not lose money?

22:03.050 --> 22:05.110
This is the price of using a new actor.

22:06.460 --> 22:08.430
But every good actor

22:08.920 --> 22:10.760
starts as a newbie.

22:11.000 --> 22:11.640
You still have to give them

22:11.640 --> 22:13.030
a first chance, don't you?

22:13.030 --> 22:13.880
You're right.

22:15.680 --> 22:17.030
I don't care how you'll

22:17.110 --> 22:19.040
be a new actress or get your chance.

22:19.750 --> 22:21.460
But you can't do that on the foundation

22:21.460 --> 22:22.940
of my losses.

22:24.750 --> 22:26.250
This is the entertainment industry.

22:26.250 --> 22:27.740
What does overnight fame mean?

22:27.740 --> 22:29.270
There is no overnight fame.

22:29.460 --> 22:31.660
There is only an exchange of resources.

22:36.180 --> 22:37.710
Do you want to be an actress?

22:41.900 --> 22:42.480
Okay.

22:44.570 --> 22:45.900
Do you want it or not?

22:47.830 --> 22:50.030
As long as you are confident and want it,

22:50.250 --> 22:51.510
I'll use my resources

22:51.510 --> 22:52.440
to bet with them.

22:53.420 --> 22:54.770
I'm sure it'll succeed.

22:58.750 --> 23:01.350
But the key is whether you want it or not.

23:11.070 --> 23:11.930
How about this?

23:12.200 --> 23:13.730
If you want to be an actress,

23:14.200 --> 23:15.960
come to the Lihua Hotel tomorrow.

23:15.960 --> 23:16.610
I'll talk to you

23:16.610 --> 23:18.610
about the script for the next movie.

23:20.680 --> 23:21.000
I...

23:21.460 --> 23:22.300
I'm sorry.

23:22.500 --> 23:24.250
You wouldn't understand
the things that I told you.

23:24.250 --> 23:24.910
Let's sing.

23:26.440 --> 23:27.300
Let's have fun.

23:27.980 --> 23:28.440
Come on.

23:29.530 --> 23:30.730
Are you going to sing?

23:31.240 --> 23:32.900
Are you singing first, or am I?

23:33.660 --> 23:34.700
You can sing first.

23:34.700 --> 23:35.300
I'll sing.

23:45.610 --> 23:48.310
♪ Stretch out your hand ♪

23:48.830 --> 23:51.380
♪ Don't have any concerns ♪

23:52.050 --> 23:54.460
♪ Open your heart ♪

23:55.050 --> 23:57.720
♪ Don't hesitate anymore ♪

23:59.100 --> 24:05.360
♪ Throwing yourself into white clouds,
you'll be drizzle ♪

24:06.310 --> 24:09.700
♪ With our mutual gaze ♪

24:10.680 --> 24:16.370
♪ you are in me, and I am in you ♪

24:18.700 --> 24:23.500
♪ Smile broadly this time ♪

24:23.910 --> 24:26.860
♪ Forget about yourself ♪

24:27.180 --> 24:30.460
♪ Love someone wholeheartedly this time ♪

24:30.850 --> 24:33.600
♪ Forget about yourself ♪

24:33.970 --> 24:36.810
♪ Stretch out your hand ♪

24:37.620 --> 24:40.420
♪ Don't have any concerns ♪

24:41.020 --> 24:43.000
♪ Open your heart ♪

24:43.770 --> 24:46.600
♪ Don't hesitate anymore ♪

25:11.250 --> 25:12.330
Ranran.

25:13.330 --> 25:15.730
Right now, the sun is shining on you,

25:16.070 --> 25:17.980
and you're glowing.

25:18.330 --> 25:19.680
How should I describe it?

25:19.680 --> 25:22.160
You're just like an angel.

25:23.030 --> 25:23.650
Director.

25:23.790 --> 25:25.090
I don't want her to miss this chance

25:25.090 --> 25:26.130
because of me.

25:26.610 --> 25:28.810
I'd like to apologize to you. I'm sorry.

25:33.050 --> 25:34.530
Among all the people I've ever met,

25:34.530 --> 25:35.880
apart from my mom,

25:36.660 --> 25:40.270
you're the woman
with the highest standards.

25:42.380 --> 25:43.290
When I first

25:43.290 --> 25:44.380
met you,

25:44.380 --> 25:46.580
I just thought you were very beautiful.

25:46.700 --> 25:47.750
I really hope...

25:47.750 --> 25:49.280
What I'm trying to say is...

25:49.720 --> 25:51.010
I like you.

26:13.550 --> 26:14.950
Who is it? Nobody is here.

26:19.740 --> 26:20.830
Who is it?

26:23.460 --> 26:24.240
Ranran?

26:25.140 --> 26:25.940
What's wrong?

26:27.460 --> 26:28.880
I want to talk to you.

26:32.220 --> 26:32.770
Let's talk inside.

26:32.770 --> 26:33.830
It's cold outside.

26:33.980 --> 26:35.140
Let's go to my room to talk.

26:35.140 --> 26:36.200
Going to your room?

26:37.920 --> 26:39.560
I want to talk about us

26:40.160 --> 26:41.050
and confirm it.

26:42.590 --> 26:43.460
Us?

26:44.570 --> 26:45.430
Confirming it?

26:47.460 --> 26:48.110
What is it?

26:50.940 --> 26:52.810
If you don't want to talk,

26:53.350 --> 26:54.220
then forget it.

26:54.700 --> 26:55.500
I want to talk.

27:05.050 --> 27:06.310
The door isn't closed.

27:17.960 --> 27:20.620
Where did you get flowers
in the depth of winter?

27:22.010 --> 27:24.220
From Wang's flower shed
at the alley entrance.

27:24.220 --> 27:25.160
As I was in a hurry,

27:25.160 --> 27:26.360
I will tell him later.

27:32.960 --> 27:33.620
Have a seat.

28:07.460 --> 28:08.260
Sit over here.

28:18.550 --> 28:19.280
Liangliang.

28:22.980 --> 28:24.180
Do you like me?

28:27.920 --> 28:28.590
Yes, I do.

28:32.810 --> 28:33.530
Well...

28:35.350 --> 28:36.550
Do you love me?

28:42.980 --> 28:43.510
Yes, I do.

29:36.640 --> 29:39.380
W-What are you waiting for?

30:37.030 --> 30:37.830
What's wrong?

30:39.180 --> 30:40.030
No, no, no.

30:40.900 --> 30:42.010
No, no, no.

30:47.240 --> 30:47.750
Ranran.

30:51.570 --> 30:52.270
I want it.

30:53.610 --> 30:54.680
I really want it.

30:56.830 --> 30:58.810
I-I really want to confirm it, too.

30:58.810 --> 31:00.670
But we can't confirm it like this.

31:02.980 --> 31:05.160
I haven't formally
confessed my love to you

31:05.160 --> 31:06.960
or gone on a proper date with you.

31:07.090 --> 31:08.050
There are still so many things

31:08.050 --> 31:09.180
we haven't done yet.

31:12.380 --> 31:13.190
I like you.

31:13.920 --> 31:14.680
I love you.

31:16.420 --> 31:17.070
I want to give you

31:17.070 --> 31:18.560
what I think is the best.

31:18.750 --> 31:19.660
But I don't know

31:20.050 --> 31:21.850
whether you think it's the best.

31:24.460 --> 31:25.330
I...

31:28.920 --> 31:29.940
You like acting.

31:31.700 --> 31:32.500
In the future,

31:32.830 --> 31:35.510
you will definitely
become a famous actress.

31:36.570 --> 31:37.350
However,

31:42.290 --> 31:45.420
I don't want to hold you back
from your choices.

31:47.880 --> 31:49.140
We can't do this today.

31:54.850 --> 31:55.910
Everyone!

31:56.160 --> 31:57.530
People from the health station are here

31:57.530 --> 31:58.880
to do the winter disinfection for us.

31:58.880 --> 32:00.140
Guys, please cooperate.

32:00.140 --> 32:00.880
If there's anyone in the room,

32:00.880 --> 32:01.660
come out for a while.

32:01.660 --> 32:03.010
It'll be done in a moment.

32:03.010 --> 32:04.010
If there's no one in the room,

32:04.010 --> 32:05.460
I'll just come in.

32:05.900 --> 32:08.030
Come on. Everyone, please cooperate.

32:09.050 --> 32:10.580
Let's start with this room.

32:11.400 --> 32:12.730
How long will this take?

32:12.880 --> 32:14.280
It'll just take a moment.

32:14.480 --> 32:16.050
Yes. You can just go back in a moment.

32:16.050 --> 32:16.460
Okay.

32:16.460 --> 32:17.520
Come on. This room.

32:19.420 --> 32:21.010
You two can disinfect this room inside.

32:21.010 --> 32:23.340
I'll go see
if there's anyone in that room.

32:23.700 --> 32:25.300
Liangliang, are you afraid?

32:25.720 --> 32:26.640
Is anyone inside?

32:26.640 --> 32:27.050
I...

32:29.500 --> 32:30.400
I'm afraid if they find out about this,

32:30.400 --> 32:31.480
I won't be able to explain it,

32:31.480 --> 32:33.080
and it'll be bad for you, too.

32:33.920 --> 32:35.660
Everyone has gone to work at this hour.

32:35.660 --> 32:37.190
Come on. This room. Come on.

32:40.380 --> 32:42.980
There are still three rooms left
on this floor.

32:45.550 --> 32:46.280
Liangliang.

32:48.070 --> 32:48.980
Come on. This way.

32:48.980 --> 32:50.110
I'm not afraid.

32:50.830 --> 32:53.430
Come on.
There aren't many rooms left. Come on.

32:56.320 --> 32:57.520
Is anyone in Room 116?

32:58.740 --> 33:01.160
Ranran, Zhuang Zhuang, are you there?

33:01.590 --> 33:03.650
I'll open the door if no one's inside.

33:07.900 --> 33:08.900
Northeasterner.

33:10.110 --> 33:10.720
I'm here.

33:11.680 --> 33:12.750
Wait a moment.

33:13.110 --> 33:14.170
Someone's inside.

33:14.420 --> 33:14.950
Alright.

33:17.330 --> 33:18.180
It's a girl.

33:19.460 --> 33:20.890
Wait a moment.

33:23.880 --> 33:25.610
Ranran, hurry up.

33:26.610 --> 33:29.410
They still have to
go to several more places later.

33:29.880 --> 33:31.170
Guys, have some water.

33:31.770 --> 33:32.880
Ranran, hurry up.

33:35.350 --> 33:36.940
Ranran, hurry up.

33:40.140 --> 33:41.350
Ranran, hurry up.

33:41.420 --> 33:43.680
Yours is the only room left on this floor.

33:55.250 --> 33:56.180
The comrades from the health station

33:56.180 --> 33:57.830
are here to disinfect rooms for us.

33:57.830 --> 33:59.030
What the heck is that?

33:59.850 --> 34:00.610
Who is this?

34:01.880 --> 34:02.570
Ranran.

34:03.070 --> 34:03.960
Who are you?

34:09.030 --> 34:09.570
It's me.

34:09.960 --> 34:10.920
Tao Liangliang?

34:11.210 --> 34:12.469
Don't mention my name.

34:17.260 --> 34:18.050
I'm stuck.

34:20.190 --> 34:21.320
Go get some help now!

34:21.530 --> 34:22.300
It hurts!

34:29.780 --> 34:30.440
How are you?

34:31.880 --> 34:32.989
Look at this. Look.

34:33.480 --> 34:34.580
It's bleeding.

34:34.840 --> 34:35.960
I'll help you apply the medicine.

34:35.960 --> 34:37.560
No, no, no. I'll do it myself.

34:37.690 --> 34:39.260
I'm afraid you'll do it in a rough way.

34:39.260 --> 34:39.650
What?

34:40.260 --> 34:41.690
You asked for this yourself, didn't you?

34:41.690 --> 34:42.980
There has been one drama after another.

34:42.980 --> 34:44.380
It's all a show this time.

34:44.440 --> 34:45.840
This is nothing serious.

34:49.460 --> 34:50.440
What a lunatic.

34:50.530 --> 34:51.790
I hope it really hurts.

34:52.900 --> 34:54.170
It hurts so much.

34:56.940 --> 34:58.400
But guys, please...

34:59.630 --> 35:02.530
keep it a secret for me.

35:02.820 --> 35:04.480
How should we keep it a secret?

35:04.550 --> 35:06.030
All the people saw it.

35:07.340 --> 35:07.820
Bro,

35:08.280 --> 35:09.840
that's one of the four great joys in life.

35:09.840 --> 35:10.860
It was your dream-come-true moment.

35:10.860 --> 35:12.500
Why did you try to escape from the window?

35:12.500 --> 35:13.160
How stupid.

35:14.940 --> 35:16.470
Beijing is so big.

35:16.650 --> 35:18.460
As long as you keep your mouths shut,

35:18.460 --> 35:20.720
people will stop gossiping in a few days.

35:20.860 --> 35:22.320
Just keep it a secret.

35:23.460 --> 35:25.390
If this had happened in my village,

35:25.420 --> 35:27.280
that man wouldn't be able to live.

35:29.530 --> 35:31.560
I can't live like this, either.

35:34.570 --> 35:35.590
After wiping your ass,

35:35.590 --> 35:37.000
you're putting it back in?

35:37.000 --> 35:38.860
There are no unused cotton swabs.

35:40.010 --> 35:42.870
You can keep this medicine for yourself
from now on.

35:43.260 --> 35:44.720
Then buy a new bottle of it.

35:45.090 --> 35:45.950
Hello, Mr. Chu.

35:48.440 --> 35:49.650
Around 5 PM today,

35:49.730 --> 35:51.090
a woman might come looking for me.

35:51.090 --> 35:52.160
When she arrives,

35:52.550 --> 35:54.010
ask her to go straight to my room.

35:54.010 --> 35:55.210
I mean it's possible.

35:55.960 --> 35:56.760
I understand.

35:58.340 --> 35:59.670
What do you understand?

36:00.280 --> 36:01.110
A pretty girl.

36:02.360 --> 36:03.290
It's different.

36:03.440 --> 36:04.900
It's different this time.

36:05.130 --> 36:05.760
When she arrives,

36:05.760 --> 36:06.480
give me a call first

36:06.480 --> 36:07.280
to let me know.

36:07.860 --> 36:08.280
Okay.

36:09.980 --> 36:10.550
And also,

36:11.480 --> 36:12.010
Zheng.

36:13.300 --> 36:14.840
Watch your tongue from now on.

36:14.840 --> 36:16.040
Don't be so flippant.

36:36.190 --> 36:36.690
Hello.

36:37.300 --> 36:39.150
Mr. Chu, Miss Shen is here.

36:39.760 --> 36:41.150
She has already gone upstairs.

36:41.150 --> 36:41.630
Got it.

37:09.530 --> 37:10.740
Whether an actor

37:11.130 --> 37:12.310
can succeed or not

37:13.060 --> 37:15.720
mainly depends on
acting skills and resources.

37:15.880 --> 37:17.170
Even if you are extremely capable,

37:17.170 --> 37:19.230
without resources, it's all in vain.

37:22.590 --> 37:24.120
Do you want to be an actress?

37:24.340 --> 37:26.540
As long as you are confident and want it,

37:26.840 --> 37:28.110
I'll use my resources

37:28.110 --> 37:29.090
to bet with them.

37:29.920 --> 37:31.380
I'm sure it'll succeed.

37:34.380 --> 37:35.320
But the key is...

37:37.360 --> 37:38.820
whether you want it or not.

38:27.690 --> 38:28.550
I like you.

38:29.260 --> 38:29.980
I love you.

38:31.730 --> 38:32.730
I want to give you

38:32.730 --> 38:34.060
what I think is the best.

38:34.860 --> 38:35.990
You like acting.

38:37.630 --> 38:38.430
In the future,

38:38.760 --> 38:41.480
you will definitely become a famous

38:41.940 --> 38:43.140
and great actress.

38:44.050 --> 38:46.110
You will definitely hit the big time.

39:27.900 --> 39:28.900
She's a good girl.

39:33.240 --> 39:33.830
Mr. Chu.

39:33.860 --> 39:35.400
This is a fruit platter for you
from the hotel.

39:35.400 --> 39:35.960
No need.

39:39.050 --> 39:40.210
In matters of love,

39:40.230 --> 39:42.230
the most important thing is timing.

39:42.260 --> 39:44.190
It's a now-or-never opportunity.

39:44.530 --> 39:46.050
The most crucial thing right now

39:46.050 --> 39:47.910
is controlling public opinions.

39:47.940 --> 39:49.460
But don't worry about that.

39:49.460 --> 39:51.590
I'm the only big-mouthed man
in the Seasons Change Hostel.

39:51.590 --> 39:52.670
If I can control it,

39:53.050 --> 39:54.030
this matter of yours

39:54.030 --> 39:56.160
will basically be under control, too.

39:58.860 --> 39:59.840
Ranran is back.

40:00.050 --> 40:04.330
[Registration Room]

40:01.110 --> 40:02.230
I've been standing outside
for a long time.

40:02.230 --> 40:02.880
I'm freezing to death.

40:02.880 --> 40:05.080
I need to go inside the house to get warm.

40:08.340 --> 40:10.600
[Registration Room]

40:13.240 --> 40:15.520
[Registration Room]

40:36.110 --> 40:37.000
Ranran.

40:37.900 --> 40:40.430
I want to explain
what happened this morning.

40:41.650 --> 40:42.710
I, Tao Liangliang,

40:44.490 --> 40:46.820
am a man who dares to take responsibility.

41:08.030 --> 41:09.560
There's no need to explain.

41:12.940 --> 41:14.010
I'm going in first.

41:44.430 --> 41:51.830
[Registration Room]

42:09.730 --> 42:10.360
Xiaobao!

42:12.590 --> 42:13.320
Xiaobao!

42:13.880 --> 42:14.770
Hongmei.

42:15.130 --> 42:17.060
They're too heavy for you to carry.

42:17.440 --> 42:17.970
Alright.

42:18.440 --> 42:20.370
They're too heavy for you to carry.

42:20.630 --> 42:21.690
Alright, alright.

42:22.190 --> 42:22.730
Hongmei.

42:23.920 --> 42:24.820
Alright.

42:25.780 --> 42:26.900
This is the stuff

42:26.960 --> 42:28.620
Zongbao asked me to bring you.

42:28.920 --> 42:30.850
Look at all these bags and bundles.

42:30.900 --> 42:31.580
Hongmei!

42:31.800 --> 42:34.690
He really misses you two.

42:35.690 --> 42:36.530
Alright.

42:37.710 --> 42:41.880
Mom,
my dad asked him to bring them for us.

42:42.630 --> 42:44.960
My dad misses us.

42:45.400 --> 42:47.550
Hongmei, Zongbao said

42:47.690 --> 42:49.780
he wouldn't wire the money this time.

42:50.130 --> 42:51.960
He heard I was coming back,

42:52.440 --> 42:53.170
so he asked me

42:53.230 --> 42:54.910
to bring it for you directly.
